Rating: 4
This was the best turkey burger I've ever made. The onion and bread crumbs give it the juiciness it needs. I think maybe the difference in reviews can be explained by the type of bread crumbs used? I used fresh bread crumbs, which makes all the difference. Dried would have definitely made dry burgers. This is a keeper.

