Rating: 3
Really excellent burger taste -- the only thing I changed was to add an egg & a little bit more olive oil to ensure moistness, especially because you must cook the turkey meat thoroughly. Result was a very, very tender, tasty burger enjoyed by all, ages 3-31! P.S. I also served with a quick chipotle mayo spread.

